description: Two single-family homes, one lot, unbeatable location! Steps from the transformative On the Dot project, this rare investment offers immediate income and major future upside. The front home was fully renovated to the studs just a few years ago with luxury finishes and modern systems, and is leased for $6,750/month. The rear home, full of charm and well maintained, brings in $3,300/month. Curb cut approval is in process, unlocking the huge value of at least four off-street parking spaces. Situated in one of the city’s fastest-growing corridors, this property offers immediate cash flow, significant future upside, and unbeatable proximity to redevelopment, transit, and neighborhood amenities.
